{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_04_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "デ、デート？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ごめんなさい\nいきなりこんなこと言ったらびっくりしちゃいますよね",
      "startTime": 5.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "デートといっても、お試しというか……\n疑似デート、って感じです",
      "startTime": 13.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "小悪魔っぽさってなんだろう～って考えたんですけど\n実際にデートしながら想像すればいいのかなって",
      "startTime": 19.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そういうことなら協力するよ",
      "startTime": 23.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！",
      "startTime": 26.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.6666667,
          "startTime": 29.7
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.6666667,
          "startTime": 29.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.45
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.45
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "わー、けっこう混んでますねー\n家族連れも多いし、カップルもいっぱい",
      "startTime": 34.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、提案なんですけど……\nあのカップルみたいに、手を繋いでみませんか？",
      "startTime": 43.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お、おいおい何を言ってるんだ",
      "startTime": 48.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんちゃって",
      "startTime": 52.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "小悪魔っぽいことを言ってみようと思って……えへへ",
      "startTime": 54.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "冗談で言ってみたら、すっごく顔が熱くなってきました",
      "startTime": 60.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、本当に手を繋いでみるのもいいのかな？\nいろいろと勉強になるかも",
      "startTime": 70.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "渚……無理しなくていいからな？",
      "startTime": 73.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、本当に手を繋いだとしても\nグラビアの型と同じで魂がこもってないんじゃないか？",
      "startTime": 80.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 83.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、それも確かにそうですね",
      "startTime": 83.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい、この間学校で友達から聞いた話に\n影響を受けてるみたいです",
      "startTime": 93.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "どんな話だったんだ？",
      "startTime": 95.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "クラスメイトの女の子に、最近彼氏が出来たんです\nそれで、初デートの時の話を聞いて……",
      "startTime": 102.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "手を繋いだ時の話がもう、もう……！\nすっごくキュンキュンしたんです！",
      "startTime": 109.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "彼氏が出来てからの変わり方も凄くって！",
      "startTime": 112.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか。どんな風に変わったんだ？",
      "startTime": 116.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "元々可愛い子だったんですけど、雰囲気とか\n表情や仕草が凄く女の子っぽくなったんです",
      "startTime": 123.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs017.m4a",
      "text": "彼氏のことを嬉しそうに喋る時の笑顔なんて\n友達の私でもドキドキしちゃうくらいなんですから！",
      "startTime": 131.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs018.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、この話を聞いてる時に\n琴乃ちゃんもいたんですけど",
      "startTime": 138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんてば、顔を赤くしてずっと\nきょろきょろしてたんですよ？　可愛かったな～",
      "startTime": 143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs020.m4a",
      "text": "クラスの子も琴乃ちゃんもどっちも可愛くて\n私、もう言葉を失っちゃって……！",
      "startTime": 150.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 154.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs021.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんはどうなんですか！？\n大人の恋バナ、聞いてみたいです！",
      "startTime": 156.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "俺の話なんて聞いたってしょうがないだろう",
      "startTime": 158.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_04_02-ngs022.m4a",
      "text": "えー、仕事が恋人って感じですか？\nでもでも、チャンスはいくらでもありそうですよね？",
      "startTime": 166.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shoppingspot-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shoppingspot-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
